// This file is automatically compiled by Webpack, along with any other files

// that code so it'll be compiled.

import Rails from "@rails/ujs"
import Turbolinks from "turbolinks"
import * as ActiveStorage from "@rails/activestorage"
import "channels"
// jquery and jquery-ui
require("jquery")
require("jquery-ui")
import $ from 'jquery';
global.$ = jQuery;
//import CSS
    import "../packs/assets/test"
    import "../packs/assets/fonts/feather/feather.css"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/flatpickr/dist/flatpickr.min.css" 
    import "../packs/assets/libs/quill/dist/quill.core.css" 
    import "../packs/assets/libs/highlightjs/styles/vs2015.css"
//import JS
    import "../packs/assets/libs/jquery/dist/jquery.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/@shopify/draggable/lib/es5/draggable.bundle.legacy"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/autosize/dist/autosize.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/chart.js/dist/Chart.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/dropzone/dist/min/dropzone.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/flatpickr/dist/flatpickr.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/highlightjs/highlight.pack.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/jquery-mask-plugin/dist/jquery.mask.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/list.js/dist/list.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/quill/dist/quill.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/select2/dist/js/select2.full.min"
    import "../packs/assets/libs/chart.js/Chart.extension"

Rails.start()
Turbolinks.start()
ActiveStorage.start()
